### =================================================================
### DELIVERIES API - PRUEBAS COMPLETAS
### =================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. GET - Listar todas las entregas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/decorator/deliveries/

### 2. GET - Ver entrega específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/decorator/deliveries/1/

### 3. POST - Crear entrega
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/decorator/deliveries/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address": "Calle 123 #45-67, Barrio Centro",
    "phone": "3001234567",
    "customer_name": "Juan Pérez",
    "cost": "5000.00",
    "delivery_person": 1
}

### 4. PUT - Actualizar entrega
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/decorator/deliveries/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address": "Carrera 50 #30-20",
    "phone": "3109876543",
    "customer_name": "María García",
    "cost": "7000.00",
    "delivery_person": 2
}

### 5. DELETE - Eliminar entrega
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/decorator/deliveries/1/